ainst.  I managed to find three guides.  Some of this content may be dated but I believe it's all pretty much the same.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://members.cohesive.net/~rtaylor/EQ/skyguide/" target="top">Adawen's Guide to the Plane of Sky</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/lordhong/sky.htm" target="top">Plane of Sky Guide</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
